agent.original_text: Based on the information provided, I cannot recommend any specific software as the document does not provide any recommendations. However, it is suggested to use anti-virus protection software and keep it updated on your computer. Additionally, using a Virtual Private Network (VPN) can help protect your information when using public networks. Always ensure to download software from trusted sources, read reviews, and check the software's privacy policies before downloading.
